Author: M0richild
Text: Was like this for a while. I work in a semi fast food semi gas station job, but the work is so busy and it's normal for people to just not eat on break. Then I cut down to part time once I started school. Went from having issues but too busy to act on them, to maintaining, to full on BED with a bit of purging and weight gain :( This can work to control binging but you have to work constantly
